 />\n<br />\n【堅。找數真漢子】呢個聯署過一百萬簽名我裸跑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1955200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1955200</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉就到啦，我哋有咩可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1968274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1968274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a0dfa798b89136519d21eddaae150a7e7b04986","tid":1982874,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29187d025026bddd304c9782b6d00925933abc45","tid":1982874,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5978f40656383314e10acde1913c3cc79097bfa2","tid":1982874,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"仲有劉馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c8f0544427dbb85a20e5d336ce0d449f98aeb3","tid":1982874,"uid":104592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:41:35.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cd583ff59579166811ab7cecf48b16d4f49832","tid":1982874,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hk